  notes:
    - "Wave 669 (uu3331): __iand__, __ior__, __ixor__ dict-presence checks for uuid.UUID."
    - "Theme: __iand__/__ior__/__ixor__ dict-presence (in-place &=, |=, ^=)."
    - "All values False — hash objects, UUID, Struct, and socket types have no in-place bitwise AND, OR, or XOR protocol."
    - "uuid.UUID is a Python-level class; it does not define __iand__, __ior__, or __ixor__ in its __dict__."
    - "uuid.UUID instances are immutable identity objects — they do not support in-place bitwise AND, OR, or XOR operations."
    - "All values are False — uuid.UUID has no in-place bitwise AND, OR, or XOR protocol."
    - "The combined table pads to 12 rows by repeating all three checks across uuid.UUID."
    - "All values verified with Python 3.14.4 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-13."
  created_at: "2026-04-13"
